  <brief_title>Open Abdomen: Vacuum Pack Versus Sylo Bag and Mesh Protocol</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open Abdomen: Vacuum Pack Versus Sylo Bag and Mesh Protocol - A Randomized Trial</official_title>
